text:
Somehow, I am tormented by vague doubts. Having looked at the area of ​​the plant. I am not sure that such a small company produces so much oil. Moreover, that it is of high quality. Such production areas cannot produce high quality and in quantity. There is no good laboratory there. Apparently they are just using bad stuff.
Now, I'm upset that I bought it in a hurry.
We'll see when using it.
But for me, it will not pass the API SP RC and ILSAC GF-6A
Very good oil. The recipe is even better than MOTUL. I speak as an expert.
